                     <interp inst="t18321018-224-person1950" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am the wife of John Brown. I lost a basket with eggs; as near as I can tell this is it-I missed it from my window, which was open, when the officer asked me; I saw a boy in the evening looking through the window - I cannot tell if it was one of the prisoners.</p>
               <p>Edwards put in a written defence stating that they had met a man who had employed them to carry the basket; he received a good character.</p>
